{"tid":2117941,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[心得]JS1204 CityU CS 分享/問答","createTime":"2020-07-21T07:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T15:45:37.000Z","uid":39894,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"35f8269265ff5a97c100faa8658f61d5cf268392","tid":2117941,"uid":39894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"鑑於2020 cohort 開始轉新hon 制<br />\n想分享返cityu cs yr1 curriculum 比今年放榜嘅人衡量返入城大可唔可以拎到hon<br />\n留意返2020 cohort 有啲course 改咗 所以可能唔準<br />\n<br />\n除非你極度唔想入三大engine爭cs major+唔介意城大名氣+唔介意要做year long intern<br />\n先考慮入城大cs (放A3啦)<br />\n揀之前記得睇返唔同u 嘅study plan / course 啱唔啱自己<br />\n城大cs study plan:<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.cs.cityu.edu.hk/academic/bsccs/curriculum/p202006/BSCEGU4-CSC%20Cohort%202020_Normal%204-Yr_2020-05-25.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cs.cityu.edu.hk%2Facademic%2Fbsccs%2Fcurriculum%2Fp202006%2FBSCEGU4-CSC%2520Cohort%25202020_Normal%25204-Yr_2020-05-25.pdf&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=ea1b1c12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cs.cityu.edu.hk/academic/bsccs/curriculum/p202006/BSCEGU4-CSC%20Cohort%202020_Normal%204-Yr_2020-05-25.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 2019 cohort , CGPA ~3.8"},{"pid":"ee5a4b1a63ab2d50748becb9411a11fd8b9ed38b","tid":2117941,"uid":39894,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"首先 cityu cs medium 大約best 6 27 , 但eng*2  所以實際當best6 23~24 所以英文考得好 可以當呢科做水泡<br />\n不過以下嘅科如果你有修/考得唔錯 你入到嚟已經lead 最少一半local <br />\nict(d) (識programming 可以唔理)&gt;= M1<br />\n&gt;ict(c)(識js css 可以唔理) &gt;=eng&gt;phy/chem/bio&gt;others<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先cs 最緊要就係programming<br />\n以我所知 一開頭大約有三成人係0 program 底<br />\n九成人連pointer 係咩都未知 <br />\n如果你有program +ict底 至少有兩科唔太使溫[CS1302 (新course ,intro to computer programming) +Cs2310(computer pramming)]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其次係M1, 佢包咗三個course 嘅內容<br />\n[cs2402+ma1200+ma1201]<br />\nma1200= differentiation (with trigo)<br />\nma1201= integration (with trigo) +matrix + imaginary number<br />\n而考試份卷 絕對淺過m1 m2 dse 卷<br />\n雖然m2 直程學哂 但因為m1係同冇m1 m2 嘅人一齊讀 拉curve 自然靚grade<br />\n只要肯溫下 操下past paper , 拎A/A+絕對唔難<br />\n而冇讀m1 m2 嘅人多數會爛grade<br />\n<br />\ncs2402= prob +stat+ 20%新嘢 有心去溫應該唔會太差<br />\n冇學過請加油 呢個course 又亂又教得差<br />\n<br />\nict(c) 幫到cs2204 (intenet application development)<br />\n但我見大部分人都識html+css<br />\n就算唔識 應該都好快上手<br />\n不過cs2204要你整個website 出嚟<br />\n但好易miss minor requirement 而失分<br />\n<br />\n而yr1 會讀兩科英文( 如果英文3 就要讀兩科補底班 唔計gpa)<br />\n雖然英文底好有優勢 但兩科都有gp pj 做<br />\n而城大盛產freerider , 想靚grade 就用workload 去換<br />\n<br />\n仲有因為cs 計入工程院, 要讀phy/chem/bio 其中一科(本身兩科 可能好多人屌鳩城大 所以變做一科)<br />\n如果三科都冇讀 就揀chem 啦<br />\nbio workload 重, phys 爛grade(入得engine 九成有phy 底 多數得cs 人就冇 識唔少人拎f)<br />\n<br />\n有科新course cs2066 係同yr2 一齊讀"},{"pid":"80683d036475ca068ea5b51d65a48646fdbf1a2f","tid":2117941,"uid":303466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f69b54d0eb408217b58ca57e04dc0522029067","tid":2117941,"uid":302348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee5a4b1a63ab2d50748becb9411a11fd8b9ed38b","tid":2117941,"uid":39894,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"首先 cityu cs medium 大約best 6 27 , 但eng*2  所以實際當best6 23~24 所以英文考得好 可以當呢科做水泡<br />\n不過以下嘅科如果你有修/考得唔錯 你入到嚟已經lead 最少一半local <br />\nict(d) (識programming 可以唔理)&gt;= M1<br />\n&gt;ict(c)(識js css 可以唔理) &gt;=eng&gt;phy/chem/bio&gt;others<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先cs 最緊要就係programming<br />\n以我所知 一開頭大約有三成人係0 program 底<br />\n九成人連pointer 係咩都未知 <br />\n如果你有program +ict底 至少有兩科唔太使溫[CS1302 (新course ,intro to computer programming) +Cs2310(computer pramming)]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其次係M1, 佢包咗三個course 嘅內容<br />\n[cs2402+ma1200+ma1201]<br />\nma1200= differentiation (with trigo)<br />\nma1201= integration (with trigo) +matrix + imaginary number<br />\n而考試份卷 絕對淺過m1 m2 dse 卷<br />\n雖然m2 直程學哂 但因為m1係同冇m1 m2 嘅人一齊讀 拉curve 自然靚grade<br />\n只要肯溫下 操下past paper , 拎A/A+絕對唔難<br />\n而冇讀m1 m2 嘅人多數會爛grade<br />\n<br />\ncs2402= prob +stat+ 20%新嘢 有心去溫應該唔會太差<br />\n冇學過請加油 呢個course 又亂又教得差<br />\n<br />\nict(c) 幫到cs2204 (intenet application development)<br />\n但我見大部分人都識html+css<br />\n就算唔識 應該都好快上手<br />\n不過cs2204要你整個website 出嚟<br />\n但好易miss minor requirement 而失分<br />\n<br />\n而yr1 會讀兩科英文( 如果英文3 就要讀兩科補底班 唔計gpa)<br />\n雖然英文底好有優勢 但兩科都有gp pj 做<br />\n而城大盛產freerider , 想靚grade 就用workload 去換<br />\n<br />\n仲有因為cs 計入工程院, 要讀phy/chem/bio 其中一科(本身兩科 可能好多人屌鳩城大 所以變做一科)<br />\n如果三科都冇讀 就揀chem 啦<br />\nbio workload 重, phys 爛grade(入得engine 九成有phy 底 多數得cs 人就冇 識唔少人拎f)<br />\n<br />\n有科新course cs2066 係同yr2 一齊讀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"我係淫底女教師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e864179a49251118f1dbfc74b54537e03e7291ef","tid":2117941,"uid":138809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:38:55.000Z","msg":"匯豐銀行今日大裁員<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fHKxOS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fHKxOS</a><br />\n<br />\nit<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a53f3b042d5e9f6e1012e60d5dc5a893c0c09a","tid":2117941,"uid":30836,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"ShittyCS垃圾嚟<br />\n唔好俾人點入去 冇得揀嘅人先會入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：苦主"},{"pid":"f4f5f26c1189dd7b2d78018291448428bb0576cf","tid":2117941,"uid":89119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:41:54.000Z","msg":"City CS 有手有腳就讀得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一年placement 幾好,俾夠時間你學翻工野"},{"pid":"bcb9beec768dd6fdf1f89bd8d351911c7f8f0d09","tid":2117941,"uid":221897,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"02a53f3b042d5e9f6e1012e60d5dc5a893c