"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"首先 cityu cs medium 大約best 6 27 , 但eng*2  所以實際當best6 23~24 所以英文考得好 可以當呢科做水泡<br />\n不過以下嘅科如果你有修/考得唔錯 你入到嚟已經lead 最少一半local <br />\nict(d) (識programming 可以唔理)&gt;= M1<br />\n&gt;ict(c)(識js css 可以唔理) &gt;=eng&gt;phy/chem/bio&gt;others<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先cs 最緊要就係programming<br />\n以我所知 一開頭大約有三成人係0 program 底<br />\n九成人連pointer 係咩都未知 <br />\n如果你有program +ict底 至少有兩科唔太使溫[CS1302 (新course ,intro to computer programming) +Cs2310(computer pramming)]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其次係M1, 佢包咗三個course 嘅內容<br />\n[cs2402+ma1200+ma1201]<br />\nma1200= differentiation (with trigo)<br />\nma1201= integration (with trigo) +matrix + imaginary number<br />\n而考試份卷 絕對淺過m1 m2 dse 卷<br />\n雖然m2 直程學哂 但因為m1係同冇m1 m2 嘅人一齊讀 拉curve 自然靚grade<br />\n只要肯溫下 操下past paper , 拎A/A+絕對唔難<br />\n而冇讀m1 m2 嘅人多數會爛grade<br />\n<br />\ncs2402= prob +stat+ 20%新嘢 有心去溫應該唔會太差<br />\n冇學過請加油 呢個course 又亂又教得差<br />\n<br />\nict(c) 幫到cs2204 (intenet application development)<br />\n但我見大部分人都識html+css<br />\n就算唔識 應該都好快上手<br />\n不過cs2204要你整個website 出嚟<br />\n但好易miss minor requirement 而失分<br />\n<br />\n而yr1 會讀兩科英文( 如果英文3 就要讀兩科補底班 唔計gpa)<br />\n雖然英文底好有優勢 但兩科都有gp pj 做<br />\n而城大盛產freerider , 想靚grade 就用workload 去換<br />\n<br />\n仲有因為cs 計入工程院, 要讀phy/chem/bio 其中一科(本身兩科 可能好多人屌鳩城大 所以變做一科)<br />\n如果三科都冇讀 就揀chem 啦<br />\nbio workload 重, phys 爛grade(入得engine 九成有phy 底 多數得cs 人就冇 識唔少人拎f)<br />\n<br />\n有科新course cs2066 係同yr2 一齊讀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"仲有因為cs 計入工程院, 要讀phy/chem/bio 其中一科(本身兩科 可能好多人屌鳩城大 所以變做一科)<br />\n<br />\n前人種樹後人乘涼<br />\n我個屆好多人同dept反映話個3科 science科冇撚用<br />\n屌撚左4年<br />\n原來依家真係減左做一科<br />\n真係老來安慰"},{"pid":"4380d44f46aaa022f6201d3faf1fd988bb11a103","tid":2117941,"uid":34764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80683d036475ca068ea5b51d65a48646fdbf1a2f","tid":2117941,"uid":303466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:20:35.000Z","msg":"cs幾難tran<br />\ngpa要好 而且要讀過cs既科(要有a range)(除非你有其他成就)<br />\n見有人gpa過3.5 但cs既科 b range 又可能面試麻麻 都唔收"},{"pid":"c8802ab3fffa0fd79cf20782d2ca93e0912cd7e9","tid":2117941,"uid":34764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"ma1200我已經覺得難到pk<br />\nTaylor series真心係惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf222943b179bfdf473c40e99dd5923f2d13561","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇program底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇Ｍ1 M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對IT好有興趣 想之後到外國搵機會發展<br />\n好唔好入呢科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分數我夠穩入"},{"pid":"a38536b1d67a209ba25431810bc171dbd4e356d6","tid":2117941,"uid":135710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf222943b179bfdf473c40e99dd5923f2d13561","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇program底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇Ｍ1 M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對IT好有興趣 想之後到外國搵機會發展<br />\n好唔好入呢科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分數我夠穩入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T19:12:09.000Z","msg":"可以一戰嘅 一年Placement真係幾有用"},{"pid":"0f2bdddd69e9f2fd9cc5fef4ea19be1d52f9c61d","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a38536b1d67a209ba25431810bc171dbd4e356d6","tid":2117941,"uid":135710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf222943b179bfdf473c40e99dd5923f2d13561","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇program底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇Ｍ1 M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對IT好有興趣 想之後到外國搵機會發展<br />\n好唔好入呢科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分數我夠穩入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T19:12:09.000Z","msg":"可以一戰嘅 一年Placement真係幾有用"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T19:20:58.000Z","msg":"我依家暫時諗到有兩個choices<br />\n一係就呢個city cs 一係就poly computing<br />\nGoogle咗好耐 應該都係city cs教啲野相對實際<br />\n但會唔會chur到透唔到氣咁<br />\n我見樓主sd出黎個study plan裏面啲野已經覺得少驚<br />\n同埋巴知唔知poly comp相關嘅野<br />\n求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bd74077d68727770933b50d5607facef812a11","tid":2117941,"uid":135710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f2bdddd69e9f2fd9cc5fef4ea19be1d52f9c61d","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a38536b1d67a209ba25431810bc171dbd4e356d6","tid":2117941,"uid":135710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf222943b179bfdf473c40e99dd5923f2d13561","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇program底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇Ｍ1 M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對IT好有興趣 想之後到外國搵機會發展<br />\n好唔好入呢科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分數我夠穩入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T19:12:09.000Z","msg":"可以一戰嘅 一年Placement真係幾有用"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T19:20:58.000Z","msg":"我依家暫時諗到有兩個choices<br />\n一係就呢個city cs 一係就poly computing<br />\nGoogle咗好耐 應該都係city cs教啲野相對實際<br />\n但會唔會chur到透唔到氣咁<br />\n我見樓主sd出黎個study plan裏面啲野已經覺得少驚<br />\n同埋巴知唔知poly comp相關嘅野<br />\n求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T19:41:13.000Z","msg":"City cs冇program底同數底預咗會吃力啲<br />\n因為佢plan你yr1,2 讀哂啲野 留時間yr3做placement<br />\n冇天生就要認真讀書 少chur 仲會有好多大陸仔屈機<br />\n但yr3 placement保你搵到工 做一年野真心唔錯<br />\n會學到好多practical野<br />\nPoly我就唔太清楚<br />\n<br />\n利申city cs廢鳩"},{"pid":"bab640bf7bf2d7cde8a1d7a15fe73e4fdc7b71a5","tid":2117941,"uid":39894,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eaf222943b179bfdf473c40e99dd5923f2d13561","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇program底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇Ｍ1 M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對IT好有興趣 想之後到外國搵機會發展<br />\n好唔好入呢科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分數我夠穩入"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:33:21.000Z","msg":"其實都唔少人冇底入城大cs<br />\n冇底會辛苦 但唔會話跟唔上進度<br />\n始終yr1 都係打基礎 <br />\nprogramming 都係教到pointer <br />\n如果你趁暑假自學一下 都夠做<br />\n除咗maths, 但我相信poly computing都要讀calculus <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然 我唔會話城大cs 係好選擇<br />\n但如果想入it <br />\n除咗三大 我相信城大cs個syllabus 比較好<br />\n<br />\n上年有研究過 <br />\n城大 data science vs 城大CS vs poly computing<br />\ncityu data science 讀比較多數 但elective 選擇比較少<br />\npoly computing 有好多唔關事嘅科 唔係好想讀<br />\n所以最後揀咗cityu cs"},{"pid":"c6a5a086e39469f4c9d70555c670c1a77073594f","tid":2117941,"uid":141809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f2bdddd69e9f2fd9cc5fef4ea19be1d52f9c61d","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a38536b1d67a209ba25431810bc171dbd4e356d6","tid":2117941,"uid":135710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf222943b179bfdf473c40e99dd5923f2d13561","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇program底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇Ｍ1 M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對IT好有興趣 想之後到外國搵機會發展<br />\n好唔好入呢科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分數我夠穩入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T19:12:09.000Z","msg":"可以一戰嘅 一年Placement真係幾有用"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T19:20:58.000Z","msg":"我依家暫時諗到有兩個choices<br />\n一係就呢個city cs 一係就poly computing<br />\nGoogle咗好耐 應該都係city cs教啲野相對實際<br />\n但會唔會chur到透唔到氣咁<br />\n我見樓主sd出黎個study plan裏面啲野已經覺得少驚<br />\n同埋巴知唔知poly comp相關嘅野<br />\n求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:38:40.000Z","msg":"yr1都尚可，yr2係會有少少chur架啦，但係handle到既，相信自己<br />\n我都係無program底 無m1 m2入黎<br />\n依家已經過埋placement，依然無穿無爛<br />\n<br />\n（如果唔介意city無hon既就入黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"4de15acbe471542cd9e96120ae3f7176708e3cbb","tid":2117941,"uid":11287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d8e64e0f99596ea74f7fc01fa460774220d24e","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bab640bf7bf2d7cde8a1d7a15fe73e4fdc7b71a5","tid":2117941,"uid":39894,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eaf222943b179bfdf473c40e99dd5923f2d13561","tid":2117941,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇program底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇Ｍ1 M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對IT好有興趣 想之後到外國搵機會發展<br />\n好唔好入呢科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分數我夠穩入"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T20:33:21.000Z","msg":"其實都唔少人冇底入城大cs<br />\n冇底會辛苦 但唔會話跟唔上進度<br />\n始終yr1 都係打基礎 <br />\nprogramming 都係教到pointer <br />\n如果你趁暑假自學一下 都夠做<br />\n除咗maths, 但我相信poly computing都要讀calculus <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然 我唔會話城大cs 係好選擇<br />\n但如果想入it <br />\n除咗三大 我相信城大cs個syllabus 比較好<br />\n<br /